{"tid":883837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金庸辭世】《射鵰》《神鵰》中港台不停拍 邊對CP最經典","createTime":"2018-10-31T06:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T07:54:16.000Z","uid":160969,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"536a9313fe9f3118333386ed8322e131952ce477","tid":883837,"uid":160969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"要說《射雕英雄傳》，香港觀眾最深刻的就是1992-94年，無線拍攝的三輯《射雕英雄傳》，當中翁美玲飾演的黃蓉，被譽為「最俏的黃蓉」，其後朱茵、周迅、林依晨等亦飾演過此角，但都被認為不及翁美玲的神似。在1958年《射雕英雄傳》已被拍成粵語長片，當年由曹達華飾演第一代郭靖，1977年，邵氏拍的《射雕英雄傳》電影，則由傅聲飾郭靖，恬妞飾黃蓉。90年代，導演劉鎮強拍的《射鵰英雄傳之東成西就》及王家衞的《東邪西毒》怪是以《射雕》為藍本。<br />\n<br />\n至於《神鵰俠侶》，電視劇最經典當然就是劉德華和陳玉蓮這一對，二人飾演的楊過、小龍女，到今日都被稱為「最佳熒幕情侶」，其後1995年李添勝找古天樂及李若彤再演此兩角，而內地首拍此劇時就由黃曉明及劉亦菲擔當這兩個男女主角。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Q9k562\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Q9k562&d=THuf5Gc%2FlHAsI2zGJgWxlnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=921d9d55\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Q9k562</a>"},{"pid":"83c7eed8f3b33561f7d75a42483ff0137da5f308","tid":883837,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T07:13:51.000Z","msg":"乜撚野CP？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61e417df5957dd5f65cf63cd3c8e147e5d54286","tid":883837,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"83c7eed8f3b33561f7d75a42483ff0137da5f308","tid":883837,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T07:13:51.000Z","msg":"乜撚野CP？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T07:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db89ab94bb6972b4d404fe4a8830a4fe1013a39","tid":883837,"uid":133529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"83c7eed8f3b33561f7d75a42483ff0137da5f308","tid":883837,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,